it is redundant with 'common crus of semircular duct'.\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3161\" xsd:anyURI\nis_obsolete: true\nreplaced_by: UBERON:0013764\n\n[Term]\nid: UBERON:3010146\nname: obsolete lacrimal\ndef: \"OBSOLETE. Investing bone in non-teleosts associated with nasolacrimal duct and lying between pars facialis of maxilla and prefrontal and sometimes nasal.\" [AAO:EJS]\ncomment: The synonym of this term has been merged into 'lacrimal bone'.\nsynonym: \"ectethmoid\" RELATED [UBERON:3010146]\nproperty_value: provenance_notes \"This class was sourced from an external ontology (amphibian_anatomy). Its definitions, naming conventions and relationships may need to be checked for compatibility with uberon\" xsd:string {source=\"http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/aao.owl\"}\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/2804\" xsd:string\nis_obsolete: true\nreplaced_by: UBERON:0001680\n\n[Term]\nid: UBERON:60005380\nname: obsolete insect pharynx\ncomment: Obsoleted because the ID was minted incorrectly.\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3051\" xsd:anyURI\nis_obsolete: true\nreplaced_by: UBERON:6005380\n\n[Term]\nid: UBERON:6001789\nname: obsolete insect histoblast\ncomment: Obsoleted as this represents a cell type and therefore belongs to CL.\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/2867\" xsd:anyURI\nis_obsolete: true\nreplaced_by: CL:0000373\n\n[Term]\nid: UBERON:6001791\nname: obsolete insect dorsal histoblast nest abdominal\ncomment: Obsoleted as this level of precision is deemed unnecessary in Uberon. Consider using either 'insect histoblast nest' (UBERON:6001790) or a more precise term from a taxon-specific ontology such as FBbt.\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/2867\" xsd:anyURI\nis_obsolete: true\nconsider: UBERON:6001790\n\n[Term]\nid: